value: A fabulous fan expansion, cost around $10 to print out and prepare. It plays really well with the regular Catan expansion, along with Seafarers and even complements Cities & Knights well. Only thing I would add is the ability for many people to start the same wonder at once.
Excellent fan-made expansion! Watch our review on YouTube.
